    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 崩溃影响了 850 万台 Microsoft Windows 设备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/crowdstrike-crash-affected-8-5-million-microsoft-windows-devices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的错误软件更新影响了全球 850 万台依赖 Microsoft Windows 操作系统的设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/crowdstrike-crash-affected-8-5-million-microsoft-windows-devices</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 18:51:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克将 X 带到奥斯汀，帮助这座城市重振停滞的科技梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/elon-musk-s-relocation-of-x-hq-to-texas-revives-austin-s-tech-hub-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家社交媒体平台总部的搬迁可能不会带来就业机会或占用太多办公空间，但这表明这座城市对科技 CEO 的吸引力依然强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/elon-musk-s-relocation-of-x-hq-to-texas-revives-austin-s-tech-hub-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 15:08:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技股暴跌加大盈利压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/big-tech-stock-slump-amps-up-pressure-to-deliver-on-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[进入本财报季，科技巨头们面临的风险已经很高。纳斯达克 100 指数经历了三个月来表现最差的一周后，他们的压力又进一步加大。]]></description>
