    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 故障导致美国联邦机构中断服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/us-federal-agencies-hit-in-outage-caused-by-crowdstrike-glitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 发布的缺陷软件更新导致全球计算机网络中断，美国联邦机构也是受到大规模技术故障影响的机构之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/us-federal-agencies-hit-in-outage-caused-by-crowdstrike-glitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 00:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 的一次常规更新如何导致全球计算机崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-outage-reveals-global-it-fragility-leaving-airports-banks-paralyzed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个小小的文件传遍全球，暴露出全球IT网络的脆弱性和行业整合的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-outage-reveals-global-it-fragility-leaving-airports-banks-paralyzed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 23:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从 ATM 到航班，史诗级 IT 崩溃留下一片混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的一次失败的软件更新导致全球无数 Microsoft Windows 计算机系统崩溃，这将成为全球有史以来最严重的 IT 故障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
